Layonya Drivensnow<br>
49 Wizardress<br>
Solusek Ro<br>
&quot;Long Live the Disciples!&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uyeldareyugami.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yeldare Yugami</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/4/02 12:12:39 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=265.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SIRENS</span><hr size=1> While fighting the dudes that drop SK armor, we pulled two holgresh and had two Invisibility to undead drop. I needed it and was happy to get a copy. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=kantrall>Kantrall</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/23/02 12:22:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=265.topic&index=23>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Merchants are your friends</span><hr size=1> OK, this is not guaranteed to work for you.<br>
<br>
On my server (Bristlebane) there seem to be a lot of people who simply sell these rare-dropped spells to merchants.  On occasion, I will spend an entire game session simply going from town to town, and checking every merchant I can for rare finds.  As a consequence, I have found a great many rare spells, including the wizard IvU, Improved Invisibility, Column of Frost, and many others.  With our variety of gates, you can get around Norrath to a variety of merchants fairly quickly.  The funny part is that these super-rare spells sell back from merchants at around 8pp each!?!?!<br>
<br>
Some of the best places I have found are the merchants in Nexus, Shadow Haven, Freeport (perhaps because of proximity to EC), and Thurgadin.  Also, the Othmir of CS seem to get a lot of the rare Velious drops too, so check those two merchant otters at the end of the beach.  Who knows what you may find.  Not just spells either, sometimes there are some pretty nifty items or rare tradeskill components (essence of moonlight comes to mind, found a whole stack for sale at a gypsy merchant in EC, as well as a stack of swirling mists in Shadow Haven and a stack of imbued emeralds in Felwithe).<br>
<br>
Happy Hunting!<br>
<br>
Kantrall<br>
48th Wizard<br>
Clan of the Wulf<br>
Bristlebane <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=kantrall>Kantrall</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/23/02 4:34:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=265.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Correction of my post above</span><hr size=1> The above should read &quot;Pillar of Frost&quot; not &quot;Column of Frost&quot;.  I know I know, &quot;Oooh, Column of Frost... impressive!&quot; <br>
